title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 173: Featuring Ned Havern
description:
On Monday's episode of Spittin' Chiclets the guys hang in Boston to record another show together. The boys are joined by Ned Havern to talk about his recent wedding, growing up with Whitney, playing with Biz and a ton more. The guys give a playoff update too along with some NHL news including Ken Holland agreeing to become the Edmonton Oilers GM. The boys also discuss the recent watch party in Boston and talk about the ups and downs from the night.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
